'''Shiratori Kofun''' (白鳥古墳, Shiratori Kofun) is the name of several Kofuns (kofun) in Japan.
* {{ill|Shiratori Kofun Group|ja|白鳥古墳群|12=draft}} - Located in '''Moriyama-ku, Nagoya, Aichi Prefecture'''. (しらとりこふんぐん) * {{ill|Shiratori Kofun (Nagoya)|ja|白鳥古墳 (名古屋市)|12=draft}} - Located in '''Atsuta-ku, Nagoya, Aichi Prefecture'''. (しろとりこふん) * {{ill|Shiratori Kofun (Higashihiroshima)|ja|白鳥古墳 (東広島市)|12=draft}} - Located in '''Higashihiroshima, Hiroshima Prefecture'''. (しらとりこふん) * {{ill|Shiratori Kofun (Hirao)|ja|白鳥古墳 (平生町)|12=draft}} - Located in '''Hirao, Kumage District, Yamaguchi Prefecture'''. (しらとりこふん)
